<div class="entry">
  <div class="entry-title">Liquid Desiccant Air Conditioner (LDAC)</div>
  <div class="entry-meta">Senior Design Project · University of Bahrain · 2021</div>
  <p>
    Green cooling alternative combining evaporative cooling with liquid desiccant (CaCl₂) dehumidification,
    designed for humid environments like Bahrain's. Awarded best project in the Mechanical Engineering
    department and the Ebrahim Khalil Kanoo Award for Engineering Excellence.
  </p>
  <p>
    The dehumidifying unit reduced relative humidity by 43.3%, delivering a <strong>4× improvement in COP</strong>
    vs the evaporative unit alone. Process: COMSOL simulation → CAD model → manufacture → experiment.
  </p>
