<div class="entry">
  <div class="entry-title">Toyota 5-Speed Manual Transmission Design</div>
  <div class="entry-meta">Mechanical Design · 2020</div>
  <p>
    Full design of a 5-speed manual FWD transmission — gears, shafts, bearings, housing, and mechanical keys.
    Includes gear ratio calculations, AGMA bending/contact stress analysis, shaft deflection (max 0.022 in),
    fatigue failure checks using distortion energy and max shear stress theories, and bearing selection from tables.
  </p>
